dable degeneracy of the proximity effect between UVB and\noverdensity. We estimated the redshift evolution of J and found tentative\nevidence for a mild decrease with increasing redshift. Our results are in\nexcellent agreement with predictions for the evolving UVB intensity, supporting\nthe notion of a substantial contribution of star-forming galaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 31 Jul 2008 15:37:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 29 Sep 2008 14:23:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
